_:N1c864e8d3c644de3857e122b8220242e <http://schema.org/description> "The Fuel Poverty Advisory Group ( FPAG ) is now called the Committee on Fuel Poverty . FPAG advised on the effectiveness of policies aimed at reducing fuel poverty, and encouraged greater co-ordination across the organisations working to reduce fuel poverty." .
